      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 27.066,
      "end": 28.046,
      "text": "ASIP's Fables.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 29.507,
      "end": 31.287,
      "text": "The Lion and the Mouse.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 33.723,
      "end": 38.145,
      "text": "A lion asleep in his lair was waked up by a mouse running over his face.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 39.566,
      "end": 43.688,
      "text": "Losing his temper, he seized it with his paw and was about to kill it.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 45.129,
      "end": 49.771,
      "text": "The mouse terrified, pitiously entreated him to spare its life.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 49.791,
      "end": 53.473,
      "text": "\"'Please let me go,' it cried.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 53.493,
      "end": 56.655,
      "text": "\"'And one day I will repay you for your kindness.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 57.935,
      "end": 68.844,
      "text": "The idea of so insignificant a creature ever being able to do anything for him amused the lion so much that he laughed aloud and good-humorantly let it go.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-013",
      "start": 69.985,
      "end": 71.987,
      "text": "But the mouse's chance came after all.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-014",
      "start": 73.148,
      "end": 82.636,
      "text": "One day the lion got entangled in a net which had been spread for game by some hunters, and the mouse heard and recognized his roars of anger and ran to the spot.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-015",
      "start": 83.616,
      "end": 91.144,
      "text": "Without more ado, it's set to work to gnaw the ropes with its teeth, and succeeded before long in setting the lion free.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-016",
      "start": 91.985,
      "end": 92.466,
      "text": "There!",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-017",
      "start": 93.307,
      "end": 93.967,
      "text": "said the mouse.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-018",
      "start": 94.969,
      "end": 100.915,
      "text": "You laughed at me when I promised I would repay you, but now you see, even a mouse can help a lion.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-019",
      "start": 102.757,
      "end": 105.0,
      "text": "End of The Lion and the Mouse.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
